<refsect1 id="clutter-GLX-Specific-Support.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
The GLX backend for Clutter provides some specific API for GLX
related calls.
</para>
<para>
The ClutterGLX API is available since Clutter 0.4</para>
<para>
</para>
</refsect1>

